<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay frames="15" />这里就像我的城堡一样啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你说招待？<delay frames="40" />
