<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊哈哈哈！</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这里<delay20 />就能推心置腹，<delay8 />
