<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对吧，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="3" />！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是叫鲜花的芬芳对吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我家里<delay8 />没有那种味道，<delay20 />
就麻烦你多包涵一下咯。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的来客真是络绎不绝啊！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正好<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />也在，<delay20 />
