	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天连<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd01" />都来了，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一反常态，热闹非凡啊！<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这种感觉也不坏呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />怎么说呢。<delay frames="40" />
像这样大家聚在一起，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉生活更有劲了，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真不错啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />喂喂，<delay20 />你们是把我家
当成集合地点了吗<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过呢，<delay20 />如果你们想来的话，<delay8 />
